um gas gasoline kerosene aviation fuel diesel and fuel oils it also provides lube oils comprising engine oils including automotive gasoline commercial and light duty diesel heavy duty off highway diesel industrial diesel and railroad diesel engine oils gear lubricants such as automotive and industrial gear lubricants and hydraulic fluids compressor oils transmission fluids bearing lubricants and other products in addition the company jordan petroleum refinery company ltd engages in refining producing distributing and transporting petroleum products in jordan the company provides asphalt products such as blown and liquid asphalt and fuels including liquefied petroleum gas gasoline kerosene aviation fuel diesel and fuel oils it also provides lube oils comprising engine oils including automotive gasoline commercial and light duty diesel heavy duty off highway diesel industrial diesel and railroad diesel engine oils gear lubricants such as automotive and industrial gear lubricants and hydraulic fluids compressor oils transmission fluids bearing lubricants and other products in addition the company offers white spirits further it is involved in selling oil derivatives gas cylinders and jet fuels marketing oils maintaining stations and warehouses of aqaba and loading various petroleum derivatives comprising gasoline  normalspecial diesel aircraft fuel civilian aircraft fuel fuel oil and asphalt in tankers the company primarily serves electricity transportation industry and construction sectors jordan petroleum refinery company ltd was founded in  and is based in amman jordan detailed description alrainbow streetamman st circleamman  jordanfounded in  phone    fax    wwwjopetrolcomjo key executives for jordan petroleum refinery company ltd engineer abdel karim hussein alawin chief executive officer age  total annual compensation k engineer hani ahmad shawash acting executive vice president of technical affairs and executive director of the refinery age  total annual compen